Coerce Object

Source: R/setAs.R

coerce.Rd

Coerce Object

Arguments

from

Class for which the coerce method will perform coercion.

bcbioRNASeq to SummarizedExperiment

Since bcbioRNASeq is an extension of SummarizedExperiment, this coercion method is very simple. Here we're simply dropping our @bcbio slot, which contains raw cellular barcodes and other bcbio-specific metadata.

See also

help(topic = "coerce", package = "methods").

Examples

load(system.file("extdata/bcb.rda", package = "bcbioRNASeq"))
se <- as(bcb, "SummarizedExperiment")
print(se)
